<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 lg:gap-8">
  <div>
    <h1 class="font-semibold text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">How it Works</h1>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mt-3">
      Understanding your challenges and providing tailored solutions to address
      them effectively.
    </p>
  </div>
  <hr class="h-px bg-gray-200 border-0" />
  <div class="how-it-works-item flex flex-row justify-start gap-4">
    <div
      class="rounded-full bg-purple-200 w-8 h-8 flex-none flex justify-center items-center"
    >
      <svg
        class="w-5 h-5 fill-purple-500"
        fill="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        ><path
          fill-rule="evenodd"
          d="M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z"
          clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <h4 class="text-lg md:text-2xl/tight font-bold text-blue-950">
        Initial Meeting (30m - 1 hr)
      </h4>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 w-5/6">
        Let’s discuss your needs and ensure the perfect match.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="how-it-works-item flex flex-row justify-start gap-4">
    <div
      class="rounded-full bg-blue-200 w-8 h-8 flex-none flex justify-center items-center"
    >
      <svg
        class="w-5 h-5 fill-blue-500"
        fill="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        ><path
          fill-rule="evenodd"
          d="M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z"
          clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
      >
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <h4 class="text-lg md:text-2xl/tight font-bold text-blue-950">
        Proposal and Quote
      </h4>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 w-5/6">
        I will follow up with a proposal to start the FREE 30-days service.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="how-it-works-item flex flex-row justify-start gap-4">
    <div
      class="rounded-full bg-teal-200 min-w-8 w-8 h-8 flex-none flex justify-center items-center"
    >
      <svg
        class="w-5 h-5 fill-teal-500"
        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        ><path
          fill-rule="evenodd"
          d="M3 3a1 1 0 000 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h2.586l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 15.414l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L12.414 15H15a2 2 0 002-2V5a1 1 0 100-2H3zm11.707 4.707a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 9.586 8.707 8.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 0l-2 2a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L8 10.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
          clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
      >
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <h4 class="text-lg md:text-2xl/tight font-bold text-blue-950">
        Kick-Off Meeting (1-2hrs)
      </h4>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 w-5/6">
        Meeting to dive deeply into the project requirements, prioritize tasks,
        and set timelines and goals.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="how-it-works-item flex flex-row justify-start gap-4">
    <div
      class="rounded-full bg-amber-200 w-8 h-8 flex-none flex justify-center items-center"
    >
      <svg
        class="w-5 h-5 fill-amber-500"
        fill="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        ><path
          fill-rule="evenodd"
          d="M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z"
          clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
      >
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <h4 class="text-lg md:text-2xl/tight font-bold text-blue-950">
        Measure it
      </h4>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 w-5/6">
        Let’s discuss your needs and ensure the perfect match.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <a
      href="#"
      class="inline-flex items-center text-white bg-blue-600 font-semibold hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-300 rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 text-center"
    >
      Get started
      <svg
        class="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5"
        fill="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
